<i>noun</i>: 대담성 [대ː담썽], 대담 [대ː담] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>대담성 [대ː담썽]</dt><br>
<dd>boldness; being daring</dd><br>
<dd>겁이 없고 용감한 성질.</dd><br>
<dd>A quality of being fearless and brave.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>대담 [대ː담]</dt><br>
<dd>boldness; daring; bravery</dd><br>
<dd>행동이나 성격이 겁이 없고 용감함.</dd><br>
<dd>A behavior or personality being fearless and brave.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>